You're being too modest.

00:02:21.220 --> 00:02:22.340
Alright. Thank you.

00:02:22.340 --> 00:02:23.180
Mr. Yi,

00:02:23.340 --> 00:02:25.060
why haven't you opened this?

00:02:25.220 --> 00:02:26.180
It's almost as if

00:02:26.180 --> 00:02:27.700
you've expected this outcome.

00:02:29.420 --> 00:02:30.660
Mr. Yi Wenhan

00:02:30.660 --> 00:02:32.940
is the lead designer at our company.

00:02:33.420 --> 00:02:34.540
It's only natural for him

00:02:34.780 --> 00:02:36.060
to pass the initial selection.

00:02:36.700 --> 00:02:37.580
You're right.

00:02:44.600 --> 00:02:46.360
[Advanced]

00:02:47.660 --> 00:02:48.860
Congratulations, Mr. Yi.

00:02:49.260 --> 00:02:50.820
We all know that Mr. Yi Wenhan

00:02:50.820 --> 00:02:52.900
is an accomplished designer
with a collection of works.

00:02:53.140 --> 00:02:54.860
What motivated you

00:02:54.860 --> 00:02:56.620
to participate in this competition?

00:02:56.860 --> 00:02:58.620
Just to burnish your credentials?

00:03:00.740 --> 00:03:01.820
As everyone knows,

00:03:02.260 --> 00:03:04.180
Starlight Jewelry means a lot to me.

00:03:05.500 --> 00:03:06.660
Jewelry design

00:03:06.660 --> 00:03:08.300
isn't just a hobby for me.

00:03:08.580 --> 00:03:09.620
It's my dream.

00:03:10.100 --> 00:03:10.940
Over the years,

00:03:11.300 --> 00:03:12.740
I've helped lead Starlight Jewelry

00:03:12.740 --> 00:03:14.100
to some encouraging results.

00:03:14.700 --> 00:03:15.620
And in the future,

00:03:16.860 --> 00:03:19.060
under my management, it will reach

00:03:19.340 --> 00:03:20.420
even greater heights.

00:03:23.220 --> 00:03:24.860
Well said, Mr. Yi.

00:03:25.380 --> 00:03:26.260
We all know

00:03:26.300 --> 00:03:28.380
you currently oversee both the design
and marketing departments

00:03:28.380 --> 00:03:29.420
at Starlight Jewelry.

00:03:29.740 --> 00:03:30.620
You're also one

00:03:30.620 --> 00:03:32.420
of the most influential young designers
in the country.

00:03:32.820 --> 00:03:33.300
So

00:03:33.300 --> 00:03:35.140
we can't wait to see you kill it.

00:03:35.700 --> 00:03:36.820
It's also been said

00:03:36.820 --> 00:03:38.380
that after marrying Ms. Song Zhizhi,

00:03:38.380 --> 00:03:40.020
you will officially take over
as CEO of Starlight Jewelry.

00:03:40.540 --> 00:03:42.020
We wish you the best of luck.

00:03:43.340 --> 00:03:44.540
Thank you all for your support.

00:03:47.020 --> 00:03:48.460
I'm not marrying him.

00:03:49.860 --> 00:03:50.740
Disgusting.

00:03:52.940 --> 00:03:55.140
Well, you broke off
our engagement for him.

00:03:56.580 --> 00:03:57.500
I was blind.

00:03:59.460 --> 00:04:00.540
But you have to admit, Yi Wenhan

00:04:00.540 --> 00:04:01.660
is quite something.

00:04:02.620 --> 00:04:04.380
I never expected
that in just a few years,

00:04:04.940 --> 00:04:06.740
he'd gain control
over all domestic operations

00:04:06.740 --> 00:04:07.700
of Starlight Jewelry.

00:04:08.460 --> 00:04:09.220
No wonder the profits

00:04:09.220 --> 00:04:10.540
have been plummeting so much
in the past few years.

00:04:11.300 --> 00:04:12.660
So did you join this competition

00:04:13.740 --> 00:04:14.660
because of him?

00:04:16.220 --> 00:04:17.500
I'm using this competition

00:04:17.540 --> 00:04:19.260
to earn my way
into the design department

00:04:19.260 --> 00:04:20.300
of my dad's company,

00:04:20.340 --> 00:04:21.980
become the design director,

00:04:22.180 --> 00:04:23.700
and kick Yi Wenhan out.

00:04:25.340 --> 00:04:26.020
Besides,

00:04:26.660 --> 00:04:27.660
shouldn't I be

00:04:27.660 --> 00:04:29.300
the designer for our co-branded

00:04:29.860 --> 00:04:31.660
high jewelry collection?

00:04:32.580 --> 00:04:34.420
You're the Song family's
eldest daughter.

00:04:35.100 --> 00:04:37.540
Is it hard for you to secure
the design director position?

00:04:45.420 --> 00:04:46.340
Yes.

00:04:47.780 --> 00:04:49.540
Getting shares would be easy.

00:04:50.100 --> 00:04:51.380
But I'm now aiming to infiltrate

00:04:51.380 --> 00:04:53.260
the company's senior management.

00:04:54.380 --> 00:04:55.380
I've just realized now.

00:04:56.140 --> 00:04:57.920
Though my family
holds the majority stake

00:04:57.920 --> 00:04:58.440
in Starlight Jewelry,

00:04:59.100 --> 00:05:00.780
the old-timers on the board

00:05:00.940 --> 00:05:02.780
are always sticking their noses
into our affairs.

00:05:04.340 --> 00:05:06.020
They seem to trust Yi Wenhan more.

00:05:10.220 --> 00:05:11.700
Then strive hard
to win this competition.

00:05:12.500 --> 00:05:13.540
It's important to me too.

00:05:23.340 --> 00:05:23.820
Take care.

00:05:24.100 --> 00:05:24.660
Easy does it.

00:05:24.820 --> 00:05:26.180
Mr. Yi is young and promising.

00:05:26.660 --> 00:05:28.500
Young and promising. Truly outstanding.

00:05:29.300 --> 00:05:31.780
Looks like Yi Wenhan
is a shoo-in for the championship.

00:05:32.140 --> 00:05:33.940
He's already the design director
at our company.

00:05:34.060 --> 00:05:36.300
Winning this will get him
a much higher position.

00:05:36.460 --> 00:05:37.620
What's there to be so proud of?

00:05:37.660 --> 00:05:40.020
It's all because of his connections
to the Songs.

00:05:46.260 --> 00:05:46.700
Brother,

00:05:47.220 --> 00:05:48.300
they know nothing.

00:05:48.740 --> 00:05:49.740
You're the best.

00:05:50.900 --> 00:05:52.060
What do you know?

00:05:53.540 --> 00:05:54.900
How many times do I have to tell you?

00:05:54.900 --> 00:05:56.140
Don't call me that in public.

