[Quefeng Jewelry
National Design Competition]

00:06:17.180 --> 00:06:18.620
[Quefeng Jewelry
National Design Competition]

00:06:19.400 --> 00:06:22.440
[Quefeng Jewelry
National Design Competition] [Final]

00:06:25.700 --> 00:06:27.860
Guanshu, this design is pretty good.

00:06:28.340 --> 00:06:29.060
Mr. Ye!

00:06:30.540 --> 00:06:31.740
Shan!

00:06:34.380 --> 00:06:34.780
Shan.

00:06:37.300 --> 00:06:39.500
Wishing the competition a great success.

00:06:39.780 --> 00:06:40.700
Thank you.

00:06:42.460 --> 00:06:43.460
You must be Baijian, right?

00:06:44.020 --> 00:06:45.660
Long time no see.

00:06:45.660 --> 00:06:48.060
You've grown
into quite the impressive young man.

00:06:49.060 --> 00:06:50.260
Tell me,

00:06:50.300 --> 00:06:52.580
is your dad still upset with me?

00:06:55.580 --> 00:06:56.540
I haven't heard anything about that.

00:06:57.540 --> 00:06:58.820
But it's no big deal.

00:06:58.820 --> 00:07:01.060
Just differences in business philosophy.

00:07:01.460 --> 00:07:03.180
All that is ancient history.

00:07:04.740 --> 00:07:05.500
Shall we take our seats?

00:07:05.700 --> 00:07:06.020
Sure.

00:07:06.060 --> 00:07:06.380
Alright.

00:07:09.820 --> 00:07:10.300
Good.

00:07:12.540 --> 00:07:14.500
This is Ye Taiting,

00:07:14.500 --> 00:07:15.220
chairman of Starlight Group.

00:07:16.340 --> 00:07:18.540
Starlight Group is a major player.

00:07:18.540 --> 00:07:19.980
I heard they're even
planning to go public.

00:07:19.980 --> 00:07:20.780
What's he doing here?

00:07:20.980 --> 00:07:21.300
Baijian.

00:08:06.500 --> 00:08:07.780
[Ji Baijian]

00:08:10.400 --> 00:08:12.280
[Song Zhizhi]

00:08:18.160 --> 00:08:19.400
[No Network Connection]

00:08:25.300 --> 00:08:27.740
Sorry. The subscriber
you've dialed is powered off.

00:08:28.850 --> 00:08:31.800
[Song Zhizhi]

00:08:48.980 --> 00:08:50.060
Has Song Zhizhi left?

00:08:50.460 --> 00:08:51.500
[Ji Baijian]
Did she oversleep?

00:09:05.180 --> 00:09:06.100
Is anyone there?

00:09:08.140 --> 00:09:09.340
Hello?

00:09:15.140 --> 00:09:16.780
Mr. Yi, I really admire you.

00:09:16.980 --> 00:09:18.300
Hope I can learn from you in the future.

00:09:18.620 --> 00:09:19.140
You're too kind.

00:09:19.620 --> 00:09:21.700
Everyone here is a talented designer.

00:09:21.860 --> 00:09:23.100
I'd love the opportunity

00:09:23.100 --> 00:09:24.300
to collaborate with you all.

00:09:24.500 --> 00:09:25.620
Absolutely.

00:09:27.100 --> 00:09:28.340
Everyone, get ready.

00:09:28.940 --> 00:09:30.220
Thank you, Mr. Yi.

00:10:04.080 --> 00:10:05.800
[Yin Qin]

00:10:09.620 --> 00:10:10.300
Hey, Yin Qin.

00:10:10.380 --> 00:10:11.100
Hello, Ji.

00:10:11.780 --> 00:10:14.020
Something's wrong.
Song Zhizhi left early.

00:10:15.380 --> 00:10:17.500
She should've been there by now.

00:10:19.140 --> 00:10:19.860
Go find her.

00:10:20.060 --> 00:10:21.860
Get her here.
The competition is about to start.

00:10:43.820 --> 00:10:44.900
Designers, welcome

00:10:44.900 --> 00:10:47.540
to the Quefeng Jewelry
National Design Competition,

00:10:47.540 --> 00:10:49.740
sponsored by Starlight Jewelry

00:10:49.740 --> 00:10:50.820
and Jihong Group.

00:10:51.260 --> 00:10:52.740
Please take your seats.

00:11:20.940 --> 00:11:22.700
The competition begins now.

00:11:22.700 --> 00:11:25.580
The theme of this round is First Love.

00:11:26.480 --> 00:11:28.080
[First Love]

00:12:27.540 --> 00:12:28.700
Everyone,

00:12:28.900 --> 00:12:30.420
half the time has passed.

00:12:30.420 --> 00:12:31.580
Time is running out.

00:12:31.580 --> 00:12:33.420
Please pick up the pace.

00:12:42.140 --> 00:12:44.460
Mr. Yi looks confident.

00:12:44.460 --> 00:12:46.300
Seems like he's sure

00:12:46.300 --> 00:12:47.980
to win this year's championship.

00:13:01.380 --> 00:13:01.900
Where is she?

00:13:01.900 --> 00:13:03.300
Her car's at the hotel,

00:13:03.300 --> 00:13:04.740
but she's nowhere to be found.

00:13:07.020 --> 00:13:08.500
Time's almost up.

00:13:08.900 --> 00:13:09.500
How about this?

00:13:09.900 --> 00:13:11.740
You go ask the organizers

00:13:12.020 --> 00:13:13.460
to reschedule for later.

00:13:13.460 --> 00:13:15.700
Song Zhizhi is
from Starlight Group, after all.

00:13:16.460 --> 00:13:16.820
No.

00:13:17.460 --> 00:13:18.340
She's using a pseudonym

00:13:19.260 --> 00:13:19.980
instead of her real name

00:13:19.980 --> 00:13:20.900
to avoid gossip.

00:13:22.660 --> 00:13:23.580
I'll check the underground garage.

00:13:23.660 --> 00:13:24.780
You keep looking around nearby.

00:13:32.620 --> 00:13:33.420
Song Zhizhi!

00:13:45.860 --> 00:13:46.700
Song Zhizhi.

00:13:56.940 --> 00:13:57.660
Song Zhizhi.

00:14:01.900 --> 00:14:02.620
Song Zhizhi.

00:14:03.980 --> 00:14:05.140
What are you doing? Open the door.

00:14:28.780 --> 00:14:29.500
Song Zhizhi.

00:14:32.780 --> 00:14:33.500
Song Zhizhi.

00:14:33.580 --> 00:14:34.300
Song Zhizhi!

00:14:34.860 --> 00:14:37.580
I will work with Zhizhi
to take Starlight Jewelry

00:14:37.660 --> 00:14:39.540
to new heights!

00:14:40.460 --> 00:14:42.500
Winning this award

00:14:42.740 --> 00:14:44.260
is all thanks to my own efforts.

00:14:46.340 --> 00:14:47.140
Are you okay?

00:14:47.340 --> 00:14:49.100
Is the competition over?

00:14:50.660 --> 00:14:52.380
Did Yi Wenhan win?

00:14:53.940 --> 00:14:55.100
What nonsense are you talking about?

00:14:56.180 --> 00:14:56.860
There's still time.

00:15:11.980 --> 00:15:13.700
Isn't that Ms. Song?

00:15:14.540 --> 00:15:15.620
She's only showing up now?

00:15:29.020 --> 00:15:30.940
Zhizhi, what are you doing here?

00:15:32.020 --> 00:15:33.100
I'm Enna.

00:15:33.620 --> 00:15:34.780
I'm here to compete.

00:15:40.140 --> 00:15:41.420
But there are

00:15:41.420 --> 00:15:42.220
less than 30 minutes left.

00:15:42.220 --> 00:15:43.460
You can't possibly finish in time.

00:15:43.700 --> 00:15:45.300
Who says I can't?

00:15:45.540 --> 00:15:46.380
You're late.

00:15:46.380 --> 00:15:47.700
You're disqualified.

00:15:48.020 --> 00:15:48.700
Exactly.

00:15:48.700 --> 00:15:50.780
Just because your family
holds the competition?

00:15:50.800 --> 00:15:52.520
[Time remaining: 29:54]

00:15:56.860 --> 00:15:57.980
According to the rules,

00:15:58.660 --> 00:16:00.420
as long as the contestant arrives
and completes their work

00:16:00.420 --> 00:16:01.220
within the allotted time,

00:16:01.740 --> 00:16:03.140
their entry remains valid.

00:16:11.420 --> 00:16:13.780
Miss, let her begin.

00:18:15.100 --> 00:18:16.820
Three, two, one.

00:18:17.140 --> 00:18:18.060
Time's up.

00:18:18.300 --> 00:18:19.300
The competition is over.

00:18:19.460 --> 00:18:20.860
Thank you, everyone.

00:18:21.220 --> 00:18:23.140
Once the hostesses

00:18:23.140 --> 00:18:24.620
have collected all the entries,

00:18:24.740 --> 00:18:25.820
the works of all the contestants

00:18:25.820 --> 00:18:27.460
will be displayed

00:18:27.460 --> 00:18:28.900
on the screen.

00:18:38.140 --> 00:18:40.340
What we're seeing now

00:18:40.340 --> 00:18:42.260
are all 25 pieces of work

00:18:42.260 --> 00:18:43.460
from every contestant.

00:18:43.780 --> 00:18:45.780
We'll have the judges give their scores

00:18:46.020 --> 00:18:47.540
and cast their votes.

00:18:52.020 --> 00:18:54.100
So, who will the judges

00:18:54.100 --> 00:18:55.740
cast their votes for?

00:18:55.740 --> 00:18:57.180
We're all eager to find out.

00:19:12.260 --> 00:19:12.540
Alright.

00:19:12.540 --> 00:19:14.240
[Contestant: Enna, Votes: 562]
[Contestant: Yi Wenhan, Votes: 562]

00:19:14.240 --> 00:19:15.220
The results are in.

00:19:15.340 --> 00:19:17.380
Two designers

00:19:17.380 --> 00:19:19.140
have received the same number of votes.

00:19:19.140 --> 00:19:20.740
They are Enna

00:19:20.740 --> 00:19:22.340
and Yi Wenhan!

00:19:22.580 --> 00:19:23.140
Give it up for them!

00:19:26.300 --> 00:19:27.620
Congratulations to you both.

00:19:27.620 --> 00:19:28.380
Now,

00:19:28.380 --> 00:19:30.860
we'll turn it over to our judges

00:19:30.860 --> 00:19:33.220
to determine the winner.

00:19:33.620 --> 00:19:35.100
How is a tie even possible?

00:19:35.780 --> 00:19:37.820
You're clearly with Starlight Jewelry.

00:19:38.220 --> 00:19:39.300
Did you

00:19:39.300 --> 00:19:40.780
rig the theme in advance?

00:19:40.860 --> 00:19:41.900
I'll expose you!

00:19:42.140 --> 00:19:43.380
Stop making such accusations!

00:19:43.380 --> 00:19:44.540
Anyone with half a brain can see

00:19:44.540 --> 00:19:45.980
Ms. Song's design is on another level

00:19:46.220 --> 00:19:47.540
compared to Yi Wenhan's!

00:19:48.300 --> 00:19:49.780
It even rivals Anne's.

00:19:51.300 --> 00:19:53.500
Fine, Song Zhizhi.

00:19:53.700 --> 00:19:55.860
Since I can't win...

00:19:58.260 --> 00:19:59.500
No need to vote!

00:20:00.900 --> 00:20:01.580
Zhizhi,

00:20:02.020 --> 00:20:04.820
since you want this championship
this badly,

00:20:05.220 --> 00:20:06.260
I'll let you have it.

00:20:07.220 --> 00:20:08.340
After all, I know

00:20:08.660 --> 00:20:10.620
how rigged these competitions can be.

00:20:11.900 --> 00:20:13.260
I don't care about winning.

00:20:13.420 --> 00:20:16.300
All I care about is you.

00:20:21.020 --> 00:20:21.660
You're letting me have it?

00:20:22.820 --> 00:20:23.660
Rigged?

00:20:24.140 --> 00:20:25.220
Have you forgotten?

00:20:26.220 --> 00:20:28.260
You plagiarized my work
in the preliminary round!

00:20:29.660 --> 00:20:31.140
Without me,

00:20:31.700 --> 00:20:33.460
you wouldn't even have qualified
for the competition.

00:20:35.260 --> 00:20:36.820
Everyone, look at the screen.

00:20:37.460 --> 00:20:38.460
On the left

00:20:39.060 --> 00:20:40.580
is my work from high school.

00:20:40.660 --> 00:20:41.420
On the right

00:20:42.500 --> 00:20:45.140
is Mr. Yi Wenhan's entry
from the preliminary round.

00:20:46.780 --> 00:20:48.380
The resemblance is obvious, isn't it?

00:20:56.860 --> 00:20:58.100
This has to be rigged.

00:20:58.660 --> 00:20:59.420
Zhizhi.

00:21:00.260 --> 00:21:01.340
Stop making a scene.

00:21:05.500 --> 00:21:06.660
And there's another thing.

00:21:08.780 --> 00:21:11.780
All of Mr. Yi Wenhan's previous works

00:21:12.620 --> 00:21:14.180
were actually ghost designed by others.

00:21:15.340 --> 00:21:16.820
I've been in a deal with Mr. Yi Wenhan

00:21:16.820 --> 00:21:17.900
for five years.

00:21:18.980 --> 00:21:20.260
Back then, my mother was seriously ill

00:21:20.540 --> 00:21:21.380
