From now on,

00:22:04.180 --> 00:22:06.260
Yi Wenhan is disqualified
from the competition

00:22:06.900 --> 00:22:08.060
and suspended from all duties
at the company!

00:22:08.740 --> 00:22:10.620
He'll wait for further investigation!

00:22:11.980 --> 00:22:12.940
Song Zhizhi...

00:22:36.100 --> 00:22:38.180
Let go of me. Let go!

00:23:15.980 --> 00:23:17.100
Song Zhizhi set me up.

