Yeah, I saw everything.

00:23:19.100 --> 00:23:19.460
I'm hanging up.

00:23:28.580 --> 00:23:28.940
Hello?

00:23:29.780 --> 00:23:32.100
I thought you had
arranged for Wenhan to win?

00:23:32.340 --> 00:23:33.500
But we didn't expect Song Zhizhi

00:23:33.500 --> 00:23:35.300
to join the competition or get hold

00:23:35.660 --> 00:23:37.260
of the evidence that Wenhan plagiarized.

