You said she wasn't that clever.

00:23:39.580 --> 00:23:40.900
That was before.

00:23:42.060 --> 00:23:43.380
After Xiaofei's birthday,

00:23:44.060 --> 00:23:46.140
I felt she'd changed somehow.

00:23:47.060 --> 00:23:48.420
Do you need me to do anything?

00:23:50.420 --> 00:23:51.460
Look into it thoroughly.

00:23:53.780 --> 00:23:55.940
I've been taking care
of my little flower for years,

00:23:57.020 --> 00:23:59.780
and now it suddenly wants
to bloom and grow its own way?

00:24:01.420 --> 00:24:02.500
I won't allow it.

00:24:08.620 --> 00:24:09.620
Song Zhizhi.

00:24:10.820 --> 00:24:12.220
Since you refuse to behave,

00:24:13.100 --> 00:24:15.380
don't blame me for what happens next.

00:24:27.300 --> 00:24:27.740
Mom.

00:24:28.500 --> 00:24:29.740
Mom, look, it's Song Zhizhi.

00:24:29.940 --> 00:24:31.700
She's really with Baijian?

00:24:33.300 --> 00:24:33.980
Be quiet.

00:24:34.580 --> 00:24:35.780
Read the room.

00:24:36.700 --> 00:24:38.340
Get a grip.

00:24:45.780 --> 00:24:46.860
I'm going over.

00:24:52.340 --> 00:24:52.900
Aunt Wenzhi.

00:24:53.460 --> 00:24:54.100
Xiaofei.

00:24:54.900 --> 00:24:55.420
Zhizhi,

00:24:56.020 --> 00:24:57.860
why did you come with Baijian?

00:24:59.140 --> 00:25:00.900
I wanted to surprise everyone.

00:25:01.340 --> 00:25:02.580
I never realized

00:25:03.180 --> 00:25:04.580
how exceptional Baijian is.

00:25:05.460 --> 00:25:06.620
So,

00:25:06.980 --> 00:25:08.420
do you like this surprise?

00:25:09.700 --> 00:25:10.740
Love it.

00:25:11.260 --> 00:25:12.820
You're adorable.

00:25:13.500 --> 00:25:14.660
You taught me well.

00:25:15.620 --> 00:25:16.700
Yi Wenhan

00:25:17.140 --> 00:25:18.420
is such a scumbag.

00:25:18.820 --> 00:25:20.020
Can't believe I actually loved him.

00:25:21.100 --> 00:25:22.300
What kind of mother

00:25:22.300 --> 00:25:23.740
raises a son like that?

00:25:27.820 --> 00:25:29.060
Well, Aunt Wenzhi, Xiaofei,

00:25:29.300 --> 00:25:30.940
you two carry on. I'm going back over.

00:25:31.580 --> 00:25:31.900
Okay.

00:25:38.500 --> 00:25:41.220
Look at her.
What's there to be so proud of?

00:25:43.500 --> 00:25:44.820
You couldn't pull it off.

00:25:45.260 --> 00:25:46.900
Don't blame others for being stronger.

00:25:48.100 --> 00:25:49.820
Men don't like whiners.

00:25:52.580 --> 00:25:53.340
Good evening,

00:25:53.860 --> 00:25:54.700
everyone.

00:25:55.140 --> 00:25:58.060
First, on behalf of Starlight Jewelry
and Jihong Group,

00:25:58.060 --> 00:26:00.900
I'd like to thank all of you

00:26:01.020 --> 00:26:02.220
for joining us at this gathering!

00:26:02.740 --> 00:26:03.420
Besides,

00:26:03.820 --> 00:26:04.740
the champion of the competition

00:26:05.140 --> 00:26:08.420
is my eldest daughter, Song Zhizhi!

00:26:15.460 --> 00:26:17.180
I hereby announce

00:26:17.620 --> 00:26:18.100
that Zhizhi

00:26:18.300 --> 00:26:21.140
will be joining the design department
of Starlight Jewelry!

00:26:21.740 --> 00:26:24.180
I hope she'll have your support.

00:26:26.060 --> 00:26:27.820
Song Zhizhi's win was rigged!

00:26:29.140 --> 00:26:29.580
Let go!

00:26:31.300 --> 00:26:32.540
It was rigged!

00:26:32.780 --> 00:26:34.220
Let go of me! Let go!

00:26:36.300 --> 00:26:37.300
It was rigged!

00:26:37.420 --> 00:26:38.300
Yi Wenhan!

00:26:38.940 --> 00:26:40.380
This is not the place for your nonsense!

00:26:40.620 --> 00:26:41.180
Take him away!

00:26:42.660 --> 00:26:43.020
Dad,

00:26:43.740 --> 00:26:45.660
if you do that,
everyone will just think I'm guilty.

00:26:50.660 --> 00:26:52.460
I have nothing to hide.

00:26:53.260 --> 00:26:53.900
Yi Wenhan,

00:26:54.580 --> 00:26:55.780
let's hear

00:26:56.420 --> 00:26:57.220
what you have to say.

00:27:00.540 --> 00:27:01.740
Everyone!

00:27:02.100 --> 00:27:03.660
I have something shocking

00:27:03.660 --> 00:27:04.900
to share with everyone.

00:27:05.900 --> 00:27:08.060
The one who accused me, Song Zhizhi,

00:27:08.980 --> 00:27:11.420
is the real plagiarist.

